<body>
<p><strong><span data-contrast="auto">PRIVACY POLICY</span></strong><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:2,&quot;335551620&quot;:2}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">Nexio Technologies Private Limited (herein as Gameonix, Us, Our, We) honors your trust while using our platform and We ensure the highest standards of customer service and a stringent privacy policy to safeguard User&rsquo;s (herein as User, You, Your) personal and transaction-related information You share with Us. Your access to the platform and/or usage of services provided on Gameonix implies you being aware of the privacy policies and having provided consent to Gameonix in regards to usage, retention, and use of your personal information in accordance with the terms mentioned in this Privacy Policy.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><strong><span data-contrast="auto">INFORMATION COLLECTED:</span></strong><span data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">We collect your personally identifiable information, such as your Name, Age, Phone Number, and Email Address from You when You register for an account with Us. In the case of User verification for Withdrawal service, we may collect additional information about User Bank Account and PAN.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">We may also collect your IP Addresses and Other information about your device from your interactions with Gameonix.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><strong><span data-contrast="auto">USE OF INFORMATION COLLECTED:</span></strong><span data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">We use Your personal and demographic information to:</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ol>
<li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="1" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">Enhance Your experience on Gameonix.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></li>
</ol>
<ol>
<li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="1" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">Resolve disputes; troubleshoot problems and help promote a safe service.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></li>
</ol>
<ol>
<li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="1" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">Collect and measure consumer interest in our products and services.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">Sometimes we use Your IP address to help diagnose problems with Our server. It helps to fulfill Our commitment to continually improve Our product and service offerings.</span>&nbsp;<br /><span data-contrast="auto">Contact information such as email and phone number could be used to send notifications to the User(s) via SMS, Email, and WhatsApp Notification. The aforementioned notifications shall be used to provide better communication in Tournaments where the player has participated in and to notify them of updates on their games.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><strong><span data-contrast="auto">SHARING OF PERSONAL INFORMATION:</span></strong><span data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">At the very outset, we never reveal or share Your personal information unless inevitable. We may disclose it when:</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ol>
<li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="2" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">Needed to detect and prevent identity theft, fraud, and other potentially illegal acts. </span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></li>
</ol>
<ol>
<li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="2" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">If asked to do so by law-making authorities or law enforcement agencies. </span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></li>
</ol>
<ol>
<li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="2" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">Our affiliates and associate websites if required to complete a business transaction You requested for.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></li>
</ol>
<p><strong><span data-contrast="auto">LINKS:</span></strong><span data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">Our platform(s) may have links to other websites or applications. You agree and understand that the privacy policies of these websites are not under our control. You understand that once You leave Our servers, use of any information You provide shall be governed by the privacy policy of the operator of the site used by You.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><strong><span data-contrast="auto">SECURITY:</span></strong><span data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">At Gameonix We go miles to secure your identity and information. We follow industry best practices to make sure Your valuable information isn&rsquo;t lost, misused, accessed, disclosed, altered or destroyed. If You complete your transaction using credit/debit cards, your information is encrypted using secure socket layer technology (SSL).</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><strong><span data-contrast="auto">CHILDREN&rsquo;S PRIVACY:</span></strong><span data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">These Services do not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13. In the case we discover that a child under 13 has provided us with personal information, we immediately banned him/her from our server. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us so that we will be able to do necessary actions.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><strong><span data-contrast="auto">UPDATES AND CHANGES:</span></strong><span data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">Our Privacy Policy covers almost every concern a potential/existing User might raise. The Privacy Policy is subject to change at any time and such changes will be updated on this page. Use of information We collect is subject to the Privacy Policy in effect at the time such information is collected.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><strong><span data-contrast="auto">Account Deletion:</span></strong><span data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">User data is retained for as long as the account is in active status. Data enters an &ldquo;expired&rdquo; state when the account is voluntarily closed. Expired account data will be retained for 60 days. After this period, User flow reserves the right to delete the data. This information can not be recovered once it has been permanently deleted. User that wish to voluntarily close their account should download their data manually prior to closing their account.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><a href="https://gametosa.com/request/?request=account-deletion"><span data-contrast="none"><span data-ccp-charstyle="Hyperlink">Click to check</span></span></a><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto"> </span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">If You have queries, feel free to contact Us at support@Gameonix.in and We will attempt to address Your concerns.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6}">&nbsp;</span></p>
